WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.655
SAHASRARA PUJA
4 MAY 1997

00:00:01.660 --> 00:00:02.660
CABELLA

00:04:19.987 --> 00:04:28.816
Today we all have assembled here to worship
the Sahasrara.

00:04:28.836 --> 00:04:50.547
As you have realised that Sahasrara is a very
important part of the subtle system.

00:04:50.547 --> 00:05:05.686
Of course, this is a great day, in 1970 that
this chakra was opened up. But by that what

00:05:05.686 --> 00:05:09.837
you have achieved, we have to see it.

00:05:09.837 --> 00:05:29.636
First of all, when the Kundalini rises she
goes to your Void, where is your dharma.

00:05:29.636 --> 00:05:40.997
And your dharma gets established at the Nabhi
Chakra, we can say, around the Nabhi Chakra.

00:05:40.997 --> 00:05:51.763
Your dharma gets established which is the
innate pure universal religion,

00:05:52.333 --> 00:05:55.034
it’s established.

00:05:55.034 --> 00:06:00.454
But then the Kundalini rises higher.

00:06:00.454 --> 00:06:10.974
Despite the establishment of the dharma, we
start becoming little bit aloof from other

00:06:10.974 --> 00:06:18.814
societies because we find they are adharmis (अधर्मी),
they have no dharma.

00:06:18.814 --> 00:06:25.214
Also, I think we are afraid that we might
get caught up with their adharmas.

00:06:25.214 --> 00:06:35.664
So, at that stage, we don’t want to cross
the limits of Sahaja Yoga. We want to keep to

00:06:35.664 --> 00:06:43.484
Sahaja Yogis, to Sahaja Yoga program and
to our personal Sahaja life.

00:06:43.484 --> 00:06:54.324
Of course, it’s important, because first this
chakra must be fully nourished. And this chakra

00:06:54.324 --> 00:07:00.783
(is) actually moves around the Nahbi Chakra
which we know as Swadishthana.

00:07:00.783 --> 00:07:11.274
This Swadishthan chakra is, in a way, very important
because it supplies energy to the brain.

00:07:11.274 --> 00:07:24.724
So, when dharma is established, the subtle energy
pushes through the Kundalini more energy for

00:07:24.724 --> 00:07:38.503
the Sahasrara. And also the energy for dharma
which was in the Swadishthana

00:07:38.503 --> 00:07:40.974
also starts flowing with it.

00:07:40.974 --> 00:07:51.114
It crosses over and starts rising in the Sahasrara.

00:07:51.114 --> 00:08:01.474
Till then we are, I would say, we are not
yet full Sahaja Yogis. Because one can become

00:08:01.474 --> 00:08:04.364
fanatic about Sahaja Yoga.

00:08:04.364 --> 00:08:11.684
I have seen people who are so fanatic that
they cannot even meet people who are not Sahaja

00:08:11.684 --> 00:08:18.274
Yogis. They cannot even talk to people who
are not Sahaja Yogis, and all the time they

00:08:18.274 --> 00:08:24.264
are frightened of meeting people who are not
Sahaja Yogis.

00:08:24.264 --> 00:08:30.524
Of course, you need not meet people who are
evil, people who are against Sahaja Yoga,

00:08:30.524 --> 00:08:38.883
who talk against it. But those who are seeking
the truth, it is our duty that we have to

00:08:38.883 --> 00:08:41.364
go to them.

00:08:41.364 --> 00:08:53.364
So, when it reaches the state where it is established
in the brain, that time, we go beyond dharma.

00:08:53.364 --> 00:08:57.684
Dharmateet (धर्मातीत). We become ‘beyond dharma’.

00:08:57.684 --> 00:09:06.094
Dharma means that dharma becomes part and
parcel of our being. We cannot lose it.

00:09:06.094 --> 00:09:16.394
Sahaj dharma becomes, within us, a part and
parcel, which is a very great achievement because

00:09:16.394 --> 00:09:22.544
then you don’t have to do any rituals.
You don’t have to worry about meeting other

00:09:22.544 --> 00:09:33.014
people, you don’t have to worry that your
vibrations will be harmed.

00:09:33.014 --> 00:09:43.073
Then you don’t catch from anyone.
You don’t catch also other negative forces.

00:09:43.073 --> 00:09:46.774
No one can harm you.

00:09:46.774 --> 00:09:53.014
That I call as the ‘completion of your shraddha’.

00:09:53.014 --> 00:10:03.114
That time, Sahasrara is so fully enlightened
that you become dharma.

00:10:03.114 --> 00:10:11.184
For example, we can give the example of Christ.

00:10:11.184 --> 00:10:15.633
Christ saw a prostitute being stoned.

00:10:15.633 --> 00:10:19.394
Now Christ had nothing to do with the prostitute,
I mean, just the opposite of it.

00:10:19.394 --> 00:10:31.614
But when He saw she was stoned, He took a stone
in His hand, and He says that “those who think

00:10:31.614 --> 00:10:37.894
who have not sinned at all, can throw a stone

00:10:37.894 --> 00:10:46.564
at Me”, and everybody was stunned. Why is He taking
the side of a protistute?

00:10:46.564 --> 00:10:49.044
He is a religious man.

00:10:49.044 --> 00:10:53.824
He should also put stones on her.

00:10:53.824 --> 00:10:57.124
But He was standing on truth.

00:10:57.124 --> 00:11:04.633
That’s exactly what happens to you when
it is established in Sahasrara

00:11:04.633 --> 00:11:06.554
that you stand on truth.

00:11:06.554 --> 00:11:16.924
There's a little difference in the; I would
say, in dharma and in truth.

00:11:16.924 --> 00:11:26.184
A dharma person might become too dharmic,
illogically dharmic. Can go to the right or

00:11:26.184 --> 00:11:28.134
to the left.

00:11:28.134 --> 00:11:39.533
A dharmic person might think he is the superior
person to others. That, why should he be trying

00:11:39.533 --> 00:11:44.573
to save anybody else, let them go to hell.
Who cares?

00:11:44.573 --> 00:11:49.874
This kind of an attitude can come in a person
who is dharmic.

00:11:49.874 --> 00:11:57.064
Also, I have seen some Sahaja Yogis, who start
new methods in Sahaja Yoga.

00:11:57.064 --> 00:12:01.973
You do like this, so it will be alright, you do
like that, it will be alright.

00:12:01.973 --> 00:12:08.064
Because they are now stagnated at the point of dharma.
So they start telling people that “you do this

00:12:08.064 --> 00:12:09.943
way, do that way.”

00:12:09.943 --> 00:12:16.934
But when you rise to the point of truth, then
you don’t do any rituals, you don’t need

00:12:16.934 --> 00:12:27.764
any rituals. You are not bothered, because
you are in dharma and here you are standing

00:12:27.764 --> 00:12:33.264
on the truth, and truth is much greater than dharma.

00:12:33.264 --> 00:12:45.163
For example, a person who is standing on truth.
He doesn’t care for any absurd ideas about

00:12:45.163 --> 00:12:49.163
religion. Even about Sahaj religion.

00:12:49.163 --> 00:12:57.094
He doesn’t care that “After all this is
Sahaja, this is not Sahaj”. He goes beyond.

00:12:57.094 --> 00:13:01.094
In the sense he sees a global truth within
himself.

00:13:01.094 --> 00:13:10.694
He sees the truth which is all-pervading.
Not only sees, but he knows and he feels and

00:13:10.694 --> 00:13:15.304
he is in that truth.

00:13:15.304 --> 00:13:23.304
So, when dharma flowers into truth, it’s a
very beautiful happening, and that should happen

00:13:23.304 --> 00:13:27.344
to all of you.

00:13:27.344 --> 00:13:33.134
So many things can linger on, if you are only
on the dharma level.

00:13:33.134 --> 00:13:40.224
I have seen people going into ego; making
money.

00:13:40.224 --> 00:13:45.374
Sometimes they don’t even ask Me and go
on doing things which they should not do.

00:13:45.374 --> 00:13:50.544
They do wrong things which are not good for
Sahaja Yoga.

00:13:50.544 --> 00:14:01.564
There is no humility about it. And they don’t
understand that whether this dharma is standing

00:14:01.564 --> 00:14:04.834
on truth or untruth.

00:14:04.834 --> 00:14:11.164
So, we have to go to the foundation of dharma
- which is Truth.

00:14:11.164 --> 00:14:18.504
As described before, it’s a Tree of Life
which has got its roots in the brain and the

00:14:18.504 --> 00:14:20.804
branches in the body.

00:14:20.804 --> 00:14:27.794
So you have to go to the roots of everything,
and that is the place where you reach when

00:14:27.794 --> 00:14:31.634
you are absolutely established in Sahasrara.

00:14:31.634 --> 00:14:45.494
In the Sahasrara are the roots of all these
ideas we have, or we can say all these ‘swarupas’ (स्वरूप)

00:14:45.494 --> 00:14:48.744
we have taken.

00:14:48.744 --> 00:14:51.634
We have now become dharmic (धार्मिक).

00:14:51.634 --> 00:14:54.164
What is the root of dharma?

00:14:54.164 --> 00:14:59.584
Why should we be dharmic (धार्मिक)?

00:14:59.584 --> 00:15:01.004
What is the need to be dharmic (धार्मिक)?

00:15:01.004 --> 00:15:06.464
There are many people in this world who are
extremely adharmic (अधार्मिक), living very well.

00:15:06.464 --> 00:15:12.534
According to, I mean, outward expression we
feel that they are very happy people,

00:15:12.534 --> 00:15:20.614
they are all right, they are enjoying themselves, while
we are deprived perhaps of all the so-called

00:15:20.614 --> 00:15:24.134
enjoyments of these people.

00:15:24.134 --> 00:15:36.014
So at the state of only dharma, things become
very important to us which are - may not be

00:15:36.014 --> 00:15:38.084
standing on truth.

00:15:38.084 --> 00:15:44.434
There are so many things like that, I can point
it out to you, that, how Sahaja Yogis falter.

00:15:44.434 --> 00:15:48.264
Even after achieving dharma state, they falter.

00:15:48.264 --> 00:16:01.534
I have seen people giving up their drugs,
alcoholism; giving up other kinds of addictions.

00:16:01.534 --> 00:16:03.484
Even their language improves,

00:16:03.484 --> 00:16:14.224
and their, we can say, behaviour is changed.
They become humbler people, no doubt.

00:16:14.224 --> 00:16:19.394
But still they are conscious that they are standing
on dharma.

00:16:19.394 --> 00:16:24.554
This consciousness has to disappear!

00:16:24.554 --> 00:16:43.374
At the stage of Sahasrara, this consciousness
disappears because truth is love and love

00:16:43.374 --> 00:16:45.994
is truth.

00:16:45.994 --> 00:16:52.644
That is the point where the Kundalini meets
the heart chakra.

00:16:52.644 --> 00:16:56.664
As you know the peetha (पीठ) of heart is here.

00:16:56.664 --> 00:17:05.824
So when the Kundalini pierces through that
heart Chakra, what starts flowing in the brain,

00:17:05.824 --> 00:17:12.354
in the Sahasrara is the truth, but truth that
is love.

00:17:12.354 --> 00:17:20.644
There is a difference between truth as itself
and truth that is love.

00:17:20.644 --> 00:17:26.614
So out of love for that prostitute that Christ
stood by her.

00:17:26.614 --> 00:17:37.914
He stood on the roots of truth, no doubt, but
what was flowing through His heart was the

00:17:37.914 --> 00:17:41.504
love, the pure love.

00:17:41.504 --> 00:17:50.244
So now when we have pure love for someone,
we see the whole thing in a different manner.

00:17:50.244 --> 00:17:58.704
We see a person in a different manner.
And it becomes very sweet.

00:17:58.704 --> 00:18:12.944
Otherwise truth can be very bitter, can be
very painful, but truth which is adorned with

00:18:12.944 --> 00:18:17.874
love is just like a flower without the thorns.

00:18:17.874 --> 00:18:29.904
It’s very interesting how a person who is
pouring with love and is standing on truth.

00:18:29.904 --> 00:18:35.344
That’s the personality you have to become.

00:18:35.344 --> 00:18:44.124
Now in the expression of love we can take
an example to understand.

00:18:44.124 --> 00:18:51.014
Supposing I meet somebody and he is telling
all kinds of horrible things about another

00:18:51.014 --> 00:18:54.384
person.

00:18:54.384 --> 00:19:01.344
So I feel tremendous love for him as well
as for the person whom he is telling all these

00:19:01.344 --> 00:19:02.344
things.

00:19:02.344 --> 00:19:13.544
So now I take to lie, a complete lie which
is a truth also in a way.

00:19:13.544 --> 00:19:17.724
I tell that person, “See, what are you talking?

00:19:17.724 --> 00:19:23.704
The person about whom you are saying all this,
has been just praising you all the time, and

00:19:23.704 --> 00:19:26.434
here you are talking like this.

00:19:26.434 --> 00:19:35.314
Now this is not the truth, actually.
But you take the help of the lie, the other side of

00:19:35.314 --> 00:19:42.364
the truth, to bring out a friendship between
the two persons.

00:19:42.364 --> 00:19:51.664
So this is what is the work of love, that
it tries to bring people closer to each other.

00:19:51.664 --> 00:20:01.814
To say things by which they become one, united.

00:20:01.814 --> 00:20:09.434
So, all the divisive methods that we have used
so far, just disappear and we try to understand

00:20:09.434 --> 00:20:20.674
what is the method by which we can join people’s
hearts.

00:20:20.674 --> 00:20:27.375
As it is you are in collective consciousness.
But this collective consciousness if it is

00:20:27.375 --> 00:20:37.754
supericial you can achieve great results like
as you have done it. Maybe you can build

00:20:37.754 --> 00:20:42.994
beautiful ashrams, you can do all these things.

00:20:42.994 --> 00:20:53.594
But when it is filled with love, collective
consciousness, then the joy is complete of

00:20:53.594 --> 00:20:57.854
collective consciousness.

00:20:57.854 --> 00:21:01.184
Now people talk of peace.

00:21:01.184 --> 00:21:07.594
You cannot have peace without this new awareness,
we call it ‘collective consciousness’.

00:21:07.594 --> 00:21:18.893
But in that also there has to be the main tattwa (तत्व) –
principle of love.

00:21:18.893 --> 00:21:30.474
For example now Sahaja Yogis say from Germany
and Austria are going to Israel.

00:21:30.474 --> 00:21:31.474
It’s very fulfilling.

00:21:31.474 --> 00:21:41.544
I was happy that they have chosen for this
Puja, people from Israel. And then I found

00:21:41.544 --> 00:21:51.104
Israelis coming to Egypt forgetting all
that Muslims have done to them.

00:21:51.104 --> 00:22:00.274
It’s really remarkable, how people get attracted
towards expression of their love to their

00:22:00.274 --> 00:22:08.984
fellow men, to other sahaja yogis. And once
it starts growing, you will be surprised how

00:22:08.984 --> 00:22:12.094
we can change this world.

00:22:12.094 --> 00:22:23.494
Most of the problems, human problems, are
due to hatred. And it is very commonly used - I

00:22:23.494 --> 00:22:29.694
“I hate, I hate”. It’s absurdity. It’s a sin
to hate someone.

00:22:29.694 --> 00:22:32.924
Why do you hate someone.

00:22:32.924 --> 00:22:39.654
You can hate the sin, you can hate the evil,
but you should not hate people just for

00:22:39.654 --> 00:22:41.104
hating’s sake.

00:22:41.104 --> 00:22:48.574
This hatred that we have is responsible for
all the problems we have had so far.

00:22:48.574 --> 00:22:56.114
Because one person becomes very powerful,
by dividing people he becomes very powerful.

00:22:56.114 --> 00:23:02.634
And these divisive things have really crushed
so many countries.

00:23:02.634 --> 00:23:12.064
For example our country was divided by the
British. Now they are having the division.

00:23:12.064 --> 00:23:15.504
This doesn’t stop.

00:23:15.504 --> 00:23:17.694
By dividing us what has happened?

00:23:17.694 --> 00:23:23.674
All the countries who have gone away from
India are suffering very much.

00:23:23.674 --> 00:23:29.574
Those people who tried to divide the country
thought that they will become Prime ministers,

00:23:29.574 --> 00:23:30.844
this, that -

00:23:30.844 --> 00:23:35.434
Most of them have been murdered by their own
people.

00:23:35.434 --> 00:23:39.324
You can see clearly how hatred manifests itself.

00:23:39.324 --> 00:23:48.964
It starts from a small point and it manifests all over.
Very clearly it can be seen in any

00:23:48.964 --> 00:23:51.244
country being divided.

00:23:51.244 --> 00:24:00.344
There’s no need to divide any country.
That creates more hatred and more trouble.

00:24:00.344 --> 00:24:11.374
In the same way in Sahaja Yoga; we should not
think of having divisions.

00:24:11.374 --> 00:24:19.914
Now we have got a beautiful land, as
you must have heard about, near the Ganges.

00:24:19.914 --> 00:24:28.574
Now people are thinking if they can have separate
houses, separate compounds.

00:24:28.574 --> 00:24:32.314
Why?

00:24:32.314 --> 00:24:38.054
You know how to live collectively, you enjoy
collective life, so why do you want to have

00:24:38.054 --> 00:24:41.214
separate houses?

00:24:41.214 --> 00:24:43.974
What secrets are we going to have from each
other?

00:24:43.974 --> 00:24:53.344
After all, whatever we do is known on the vibrations,
you cannot hide anything. So why have separate

00:24:53.344 --> 00:24:54.444
houses.

00:24:54.444 --> 00:25:01.254
Why do you want to have some privacy?
Because in Sahaja Yoga, there is no privacy.

00:25:01.254 --> 00:25:09.964
We know about everyone, ‘what are they up to,
what are their problems, what chakras they

00:25:09.964 --> 00:25:11.034
are catching.

00:25:11.034 --> 00:25:12.114
Isn’t it?

00:25:12.114 --> 00:25:16.344
So there is no secret about anything in Sahaja
Yoga.

00:25:16.344 --> 00:25:22.774
Everyone knows about everyone. So, what’s
the use of having privacy also,

00:25:22.774 --> 00:25:23.774
I can’t understand

00:25:23.774 --> 00:25:31.314
It’s like this, you see, still the mind is
working like that.

00:25:31.314 --> 00:25:35.004
Then they are thinking of inheritance.

00:25:35.004 --> 00:25:43.924
All right, I was saying that you can have inheritance,
but if your son is not a Sahaja Yogi, what

00:25:43.924 --> 00:25:44.924
to do?

00:25:44.924 --> 00:25:52.844
We cannot keep a culprit there, to trouble
everyone.

00:25:52.844 --> 00:26:01.474
It is not the rules and regulations that are
going to keep you happy and joined together,

00:26:01.474 --> 00:26:08.054
but it is the pure, collective consciousness
and its love.

00:26:08.054 --> 00:26:15.844
Because as you know we have no proper organisations,
we have no clergy-ship, we have nothing like

00:26:15.844 --> 00:26:16.844
that.

00:26:16.844 --> 00:26:22.534
Leaders also can shift, more times than Ganges
river can shift its course.

00:26:22.534 --> 00:26:24.024
So there is nothing like that.

00:26:24.024 --> 00:26:30.454
It’s all on a shifty sand we are standing,
all the time, and Your Mother is another one

00:26:30.454 --> 00:26:33.794
who tries all kinds of tricks.

00:26:33.794 --> 00:26:46.514
The reason is, I want you to stand on rocks.
And this rock is emitting love; is emitting

00:26:46.514 --> 00:26:58.444
that Divine Love. And the joy of that love
is really so beautiful.

00:26:58.444 --> 00:27:04.774
For example people would like to have their
separate bathrooms, specially Indian. Suddenly

00:27:04.774 --> 00:27:09.874
they have become Britishers and Britishers
have become Indians.

00:27:09.874 --> 00:27:16.334
Indians want to have their separate bathrooms
- I don’t know why. And this is a very

00:27:16.334 --> 00:27:18.884
common disease with Indians,

00:27:18.884 --> 00:27:24.744
And it is also spreading to other people, I
feel sometimes, that they want to have their

00:27:24.744 --> 00:27:27.604
separate bathrooms.

00:27:27.604 --> 00:27:30.214
In a collective life there is no need.

00:27:30.214 --> 00:27:37.224
You don’t even know; if you ask Me,
I wouldn’t even know if I have been to bathroom or not.

00:27:37.224 --> 00:27:39.684
Just go there -, come back, finished.

00:27:39.684 --> 00:27:45.144
I have no time for all that.

00:27:45.144 --> 00:27:54.954
In the same way, you also should have a concept
of a society which is living like a ocean.

00:27:54.954 --> 00:28:01.764
If ocean rises – they rise, if falls – they fall.
Just one unison of love.

00:28:02.714 --> 00:28:12.984
I am expecting that kind of a society at the
foothill of Himalayas. And I am sure you, all

00:28:12.984 --> 00:28:20.134
of you realise that, Himalaya being the Sahasrara
of the world.

00:28:20.134 --> 00:28:28.774
Luckily I wanted it to be done before the
Sahasrar puja, and it is done; with the blessings

00:28:28.774 --> 00:28:31.384
of Himalayas, I should say.

00:28:31.384 --> 00:28:39.434
The Himalaya is also like a Sahasrara where
the Kundalini has risen, where the vibrations

00:28:39.434 --> 00:28:44.554
have come out. And in the sky you can see
the vibrations.

00:28:44.554 --> 00:28:55.984
But this Himalaya is ruled by a wrathful God
called Shiva! That’s the dangerous part

00:28:55.984 --> 00:28:57.804
of it.

00:28:57.804 --> 00:29:02.364
So, we have to be very, very careful.

00:29:02.364 --> 00:29:17.514
If we try to play around, if we try to
take to hatred among ourselves, take to divisive

00:29:17.514 --> 00:29:28.114
methods, take to something that is not Sahaj,
this wrathful God is sitting on our head.

00:29:28.114 --> 00:29:34.404
He is also in Mecca. This is ‘Makkeshwar Shiv’
there.

00:29:34.404 --> 00:29:40.024
If you try to misbehave, he comes out with
his wrathfulness.

00:29:40.024 --> 00:29:46.714
Anywhere you are, you have to be
very careful that this Shiva is everywhere.

00:29:46.714 --> 00:29:59.465
Like one of these lingas of Shiva is in ’Parali Baijanath’ (परळी बैजनाथ),
that is in Maharashtra, Alahathur, and there

00:29:59.465 --> 00:30:07.394
people started another kind of sahaja yoga.
Also they were drinking on the day of the

00:30:07.394 --> 00:30:21.714
Shri Ganesha’s visarjan (विसर्जन),, so the wrath
of Shiva-linga came and there was such a big,

00:30:21.714 --> 00:30:24.434
huge earthquake.

00:30:24.434 --> 00:30:34.704
Many people were lost. But none of the Sahaja
Yogis, and their centre was saved completely.

00:30:34.704 --> 00:30:41.464
Now we had a big fire also, as you know last
time (in Ganapatipule), and nothing happened to you, you are

00:30:41.464 --> 00:30:42.804
under protection.

00:30:42.804 --> 00:30:45.774
You are all the time protected.

00:30:45.774 --> 00:30:51.884
There was no wrath of Shiva that could work
out anything.

00:30:51.884 --> 00:30:55.604
Fire could not do anything to you because
you are under protection.

00:30:55.604 --> 00:31:00.484
But this protection is your Mother’s love.

00:31:00.484 --> 00:31:07.324
It’s not anything else but the love of your
Mother, which is very powerful and which

00:31:07.324 --> 00:31:10.554
is protecting you and helping you.

00:31:10.554 --> 00:31:17.743
In the same way you develop that kind of love
for others, for other sahaja yogis, for other

00:31:17.743 --> 00:31:23.184
people, for other things, for this Mother
Earth, for all that.

00:31:23.184 --> 00:31:31.124
Your love can not only protect you, but protect
others also.

00:31:31.124 --> 00:31:37.504
Your attention as long as it is on yourself
will start becoming smaller and smaller.

00:31:37.504 --> 00:31:42.994
“I should have this, I should have that, I
like this, I like that.”

00:31:42.994 --> 00:31:46.254
- all these topics will fall.

00:31:46.254 --> 00:31:51.424
You’ll never say “I like this’.

00:31:51.424 --> 00:31:53.684
No question.

00:31:53.684 --> 00:31:54.754
What do I like?

00:31:54.754 --> 00:32:03.384
It’s difficult for Me to decide, if I like anything. “This I like, that I like. I like

00:32:03.384 --> 00:32:05.304
to be this way.”

00:32:05.304 --> 00:32:06.344
Who are you?

00:32:06.344 --> 00:32:09.834
cAsk yourself the question.

00:32:09.834 --> 00:32:12.384
Who are you?

00:32:12.384 --> 00:32:22.384
If you are the Pure Spirit, it is nothing but love.
And in love you think of others, the

00:32:22.384 --> 00:32:29.654
problems of others, you try to make others
comfortable. You try to look after others

00:32:29.654 --> 00:32:35.104
and you don’t just look after yourself and
bothered about yourself.

00:32:35.104 --> 00:32:37.204
This is what you have to reach.

00:32:37.204 --> 00:32:43.164
Though you may be dharmic, you may be in every
way sahaj, but still, unless and until you

00:32:43.164 --> 00:32:52.594
reach that state in your Sahasrara, I wouldn’t
say that you are all right.

00:32:52.594 --> 00:32:54.454
You have to work it out.

00:32:54.454 --> 00:33:01.984
For that of course meditation is very important,
but the thing that stops it, is your mind.

00:33:01.984 --> 00:33:05.784
Is your mind that goes on telling you.

00:33:05.784 --> 00:33:09.824
All the time you watch your mind, how it tries
to guide you.

00:33:09.824 --> 00:33:17.264
How it tries to tell you - “now what about
me, what about my house? What about my children,

00:33:17.264 --> 00:33:20.534
what about my country?”

00:33:20.534 --> 00:33:26.844
Like that you go on “My, my, my, my, my,”
ultimately you end up into nothing.

00:33:26.844 --> 00:33:33.714
But when you say, “You, you, you”…
Kabira has said a beautiful thing about it.

00:33:33.714 --> 00:33:44.164
He says that – when the goat is living, it is
saying (in Hindi) “Mai , mai, mai” means “I,

00:33:44.164 --> 00:33:45.514
I, I.

00:33:45.514 --> 00:33:54.493
But it dies, then they take out the intestines
and put it on a dhunki (धुनकी), which they put it

00:33:54.493 --> 00:33:58.564
for the cleaning of the cotton,

00:33:58.564 --> 00:34:05.243
And that time, what does this dhunki (धुनकी) says?
“Tuhi, tuhi, tuhi - You are the one, you are,

00:34:05.243 --> 00:34:11.294
you are, you are.” And that echoes all over.

00:34:11.294 --> 00:34:16.564
In the same way you have to think from other’s
point of view.

00:34:16.564 --> 00:34:24.134
First of all tuhi when you say; you say it
to your Guru or to God that “You are!

00:34:24.134 --> 00:34:31.054
I am no more, I am dissolved, I am finished, I
(am) become one with this ocean of love.

00:34:31.054 --> 00:34:40.814
And then you say to others,
“You are, you are” – that is Sahaj Culture.

00:34:40.814 --> 00:34:49.664
See, so, lots of falsehood will
fall off. Falsehood that surrenders you and others.

00:34:49.664 --> 00:34:58.264
Like people try falsehood by saying something:
“I love you very much”, and on the back

00:34:58.264 --> 00:35:01.234
they plan something very bad.

00:35:01.234 --> 00:35:03.993
They can do anything.

00:35:03.993 --> 00:35:08.504
Not Sahaja Yogis, they don’t do it, I must
say that they have reached the stage where

00:35:08.504 --> 00:35:09.994
they don’t do it.

00:35:09.994 --> 00:35:14.104
But still if they don’t do it, they are conscious
of it.

00:35:14.104 --> 00:35:21.984
All the time they are conscious,
“We don’t do this, we don’t drink. So what? “We don’t

00:35:21.984 --> 00:35:23.594
fuss about food.”

00:35:23.594 --> 00:35:30.324
I mean, all their things they have achieved,
they are very proud of it, you see, very proud

00:35:30.324 --> 00:35:33.574
- that “We are like this, we are that.”

00:35:33.574 --> 00:35:41.124
You see, because you are the pure Spirit,
because you are that, so you have become that.

00:35:41.124 --> 00:35:45.304
How can you take pride in something what you
are?

00:35:45.304 --> 00:35:50.384
Like somebody asked me, “Don’t you feel very
proud that you are Adi Shakti?

00:35:50.384 --> 00:35:54.134
I said ‘What?’

00:35:54.134 --> 00:35:56.024
I couldn’t understand the question.

00:35:56.024 --> 00:36:01.795
I said, " See now, if I’m Adi Shakti, what is
there to be proud? Because I am that.

00:36:01.795 --> 00:36:03.434
What is there to be proud?”

00:36:03.434 --> 00:36:09.484
If I was not that, then I would be proud of
it, but I was. So what is there to be proud of?

00:36:09.484 --> 00:36:10.554
of.

00:36:10.554 --> 00:36:18.084
Like the sun, you see, it shines, is not proud that “I am the sun!” Or if you are born,

00:36:18.084 --> 00:36:27.064
say, with your eyes and nose, a face like
a human being, you are not proud, “I'm a human

00:36:27.064 --> 00:36:30.454
being, I'm a human being!” Are you proud?

00:36:30.454 --> 00:36:39.233
In the same way if you are that - what you are,
you are not proud, you are not conscious of about it;

00:36:39.233 --> 00:36:42.434
not at all conscious.

00:36:42.434 --> 00:36:46.354
I mean, I never tell Myself I am Adi Shakti,
there is no need to tell.

00:36:46.354 --> 00:36:47.954
But it is so, what to do?

00:36:47.954 --> 00:36:53.504
Now God has chosen Me, I should say, to be
the Adi Shakti, alright, I can have it.

00:36:53.504 --> 00:36:59.284
But I just don’t know what is there,
as if like some people think that sahaja yoga

00:36:59.284 --> 00:37:06.464
has been bestowed upon them like some Lordship
or something like that; [it’s] not that.

00:37:06.464 --> 00:37:16.154
It is what you have become! When you become,
one must understand, that you have become that.

00:37:16.154 --> 00:37:25.993
Like supposing a stone becomes gold.
Then it is gold. It won’t be proud that “I’m

00:37:25.993 --> 00:37:26.993
gold” - gold is gold.

00:37:26.993 --> 00:37:30.314
Why will it be proud of that?

00:37:30.314 --> 00:37:39.684
In the same way this consciousness of being
a Sahaja Yogi drops off.

00:37:39.684 --> 00:37:46.204
Still it lingers, so one has to be careful
that once you are a sahaja yogi, you are a

00:37:46.204 --> 00:37:47.844
sahaja yogi - so what?

00:37:47.844 --> 00:37:52.774
“I am a sahaji”; so what?
Nothing so great.

00:37:52.774 --> 00:37:59.664
It’s like saying that “I have a nose,” you
see. To be proud of saying “I have a nose.

00:37:59.664 --> 00:38:05.363
Nose is already there, what is there to be proud of?
But this pride has to go away.

00:38:05.363 --> 00:38:13.243
That’s very important to realise, that “I’m
not there, I am no more. I am one of the

00:38:13.243 --> 00:38:20.363
whole; become the ocean, this drop of mine.
I don’t know if there are any boundaries

00:38:20.363 --> 00:38:21.914
left in me.”

00:38:21.914 --> 00:38:28.294
This kind of consciousness develops in you,
when your consciousness is filled with joy only.

00:38:28.294 --> 00:38:34.964
Just with joy and bubbling with love. Bubbling
with love.

00:38:34.964 --> 00:38:45.833
You go on, you see, expressing your love, whether
you talk or you don’t talk; whether you

00:38:45.833 --> 00:38:56.144
say about it or you don’t; whether you are
smiling or not; this joy is in your heart.

00:38:56.144 --> 00:39:09.894
Now the Heart Chakra here, the peetha of the
heart chakra, gets filled with the light of truth.

00:39:09.894 --> 00:39:18.144
But the truth is not such an absurd thing
that we know of as truth is.

00:39:18.144 --> 00:39:21.704
Somebody asked Me “What is the truth?”

00:39:21.704 --> 00:39:31.694
So I said that “It was written, long time back that -
you should speak he truth and speak

00:39:31.694 --> 00:39:38.834
something that people will like.”
– “satyam vadet, priyam vadet (सत्यम् वदेत्, प्रियं वदेत्).”

00:39:38.834 --> 00:39:42.714
Then people said “How can you meet these two things?

00:39:42.714 --> 00:39:50.764
Truth may not be palatable and could be something
that you say which people like, and maybe

00:39:50.764 --> 00:39:55.284
false, so how to make these two things meet?”

00:39:55.284 --> 00:40:04.444
So Krishna gave a very good answer. He said, it’s like this-
“satyam vadet, hitam vadet,

00:40:04.444 --> 00:40:05.444
priyam vadet (सत्यम् वदेत्, हितं वदेत्, प्रियं वदेत्);

00:40:05.444 --> 00:40:13.004
You say the truth; truth you must say, but
that truth should be good or should be liked

00:40:13.004 --> 00:40:21.614
or should be appreciated or should be nourishing
for your Spirit, by which there is benevolence

00:40:21.614 --> 00:40:28.134
which creates benevolence. And then it has
To be ‘priy (प्रिय)’.”

00:40:28.134 --> 00:40:34.604
In the beginning people may not like and
say that, “He said horrible things to me’

00:40:34.604 --> 00:40:42.734
or whatever it is. But at the end of it he will
say that “See, it’s so good that this was

00:40:42.734 --> 00:40:46.704
said to me that I have done something perfect.”

00:40:46.704 --> 00:40:54.394
But in any case, there is no need to say something
very harsh or hard to anyone.

00:40:54.394 --> 00:41:00.524
That is not your job to go on correcting all
the rest of the people.

00:41:00.524 --> 00:41:05.284
To begin with, many sahaja yogis I have seen,
have been saying, “You’ve got this chakra

00:41:05.284 --> 00:41:07.484
caught up, you have got that chakra caught
up!”

00:41:07.484 --> 00:41:11.194
All this is the play of ego.

00:41:11.194 --> 00:41:16.254
You have no business to condemn anyone.
You have come from such a condemned condition

00:41:16.254 --> 00:41:19.484
yourself, so why are you condemning others?

00:41:19.484 --> 00:41:26.724
Only thing is, if you are capable, if you are
equipped, if you are matured enough in sahaja

00:41:26.724 --> 00:41:34.914
yoga, then you will just take it up as a great
challenge of love. And you will do it.

00:41:34.914 --> 00:41:39.355
But you won’t go on condemning that person,
finding faults with that person, it’s a

00:41:39.355 --> 00:41:44.084
very good excuse if you don’t want to do
it.

00:41:44.084 --> 00:41:50.064
Supposing somebody is sick, and the doctor
doesn’t know how to cure, so what does he

00:41:50.064 --> 00:41:51.064
do?

00:41:51.064 --> 00:41:56.874
He says you see, you are sick because this
happened, because you went in the cold,

00:41:56.874 --> 00:42:02.674
because this…” “Arey baba, yes! But now I am sick.
So now what about curing me?

00:42:02.674 --> 00:42:07.794
No, because you did this, because you did
that, you should not have done this.

00:42:07.794 --> 00:42:10.694
All about the past mistakes he will go on.

00:42:10.694 --> 00:42:17.404
In the same way, we go on, that “You did like
this, you were like this, you went to the

00:42:17.404 --> 00:42:22.654
phalana (फलाना) guru, you did this kind of a mistake;
that’s why you are like this.”

00:42:22.654 --> 00:42:27.634
No, don’t tell him anything! Just work it
out and it works.

00:42:27.634 --> 00:42:34.293
Of course, you can ask, if he has been to some
guru, but don’t condemn, don’t criticise,

00:42:34.293 --> 00:42:40.204
there is no need to condemn anybody for what
mistakes they have committed.

00:42:40.204 --> 00:42:45.464
This is all coming from the consciousness
that you are better equipped, that you have

00:42:45.464 --> 00:42:46.914
all the knowledge.

00:42:46.914 --> 00:42:53.404
You have, you are very knowledgeable people, I
must say, very knowledgeable.

00:42:53.404 --> 00:43:03.004
You are the gnostics, all that I accept.
But as long as you are aware of it, you are not.

00:43:03.004 --> 00:43:11.624
Once you are not aware of it, then you are
that, what is called Sahaja Yogi.

00:43:11.624 --> 00:43:18.454
So I would expect all of you to have this
new development in their Sahasrara, in your

00:43:18.454 --> 00:43:21.484
Sahasrara, in everybody’s Sahasrara.

00:43:21.484 --> 00:43:23.384
We have to think of the whole world.

00:43:23.384 --> 00:43:27.435
We cannot just think of Sahaja Yogis and also
about the seekers.

00:43:27.435 --> 00:43:32.025
Seekers are there, all right, but what about
the rest?

00:43:32.025 --> 00:43:36.074
There are so many problems they have, and so many
things are to be done.

00:43:36.074 --> 00:43:41.614
For example, now we have a problem in India
of poverty.

00:43:41.614 --> 00:43:44.404
So, I am trying to do something for them.

00:43:44.404 --> 00:43:47.284
You have problems in your countries.

00:43:47.284 --> 00:43:50.264
You should find out what problems there are.

00:43:50.264 --> 00:43:56.793
You can start some sort of a movement for
them, try to help them as far as possible.

00:43:56.793 --> 00:44:03.674
It’s not missionary-like, that you convert
somebody for some sort of a reward, or for

00:44:03.674 --> 00:44:09.234
some name you have to do it. You just do it
for your pleasure. Because it’s your pleasure

00:44:09.234 --> 00:44:10.384
to do it.

00:44:10.384 --> 00:44:15.214
That’s how you will go to the society and
you won’t be afraid that you will be caught

00:44:15.214 --> 00:44:16.214
up.

00:44:16.214 --> 00:44:21.793
I know of one couple when I asked them,
“Why don’t you start working it out.

00:44:21.793 --> 00:44:24.884
So they said ‘Mother we are afraid our ego
will come back’.

00:44:24.884 --> 00:44:29.794
They are afraid of themselves only - That their
ego will come back.

00:44:29.794 --> 00:44:36.264
So all these problems should be dropped out
and you should reach that state where you

00:44:36.264 --> 00:44:42.634
don’t have all these fears, all these
nonsensical ideas about yourself.

00:44:42.634 --> 00:44:44.744
You are powerful.

00:44:44.744 --> 00:44:46.754
You have powers.

00:44:46.754 --> 00:44:50.624
Not only that, but you have been specially
bestowed with those powers.

00:44:50.624 --> 00:44:54.254
But if you don’t use it, then what are
you?

00:44:54.254 --> 00:45:01.984
If the lamp is not enlightened, what is this
lamp for? just for decoration?

00:45:01.984 --> 00:45:08.783
So this has to be used. And this has to be
used without feeling that awareness within

00:45:08.783 --> 00:45:15.864
you that you are something great, better than
others, something selected or also they say

00:45:15.864 --> 00:45:19.754
that we are chosen.

00:45:19.754 --> 00:45:26.874
So, this can spread very fast with such grace
and understanding.

00:45:26.874 --> 00:45:32.034
All kinds of stupid people are there, it’s
alright, you know they are stupid. Just laugh

00:45:32.034 --> 00:45:36.984
at them, make fun of them and that’s how
you can solve the problem.

00:45:36.984 --> 00:45:43.364
But even that, you should do it in such a
way that you don’t hurt them. That whatever

00:45:43.364 --> 00:45:48.454
you do, you should see from the results, what
works out.

00:45:48.454 --> 00:46:00.654
Results should be such that you should
see how it works out.

00:46:00.654 --> 00:46:05.144
With some people - that’s the intelligence,
I think, that’s the superior intelligence

00:46:05.144 --> 00:46:11.824
by which you know how to say things, what
to say things, how to work it out.

00:46:11.824 --> 00:46:22.154
Love, this Divine love gives you a complete
control over yourself. And you know everything,

00:46:22.154 --> 00:46:28.314
how to behave, how to talk to people, how
to manage them.

00:46:28.314 --> 00:46:36.264
I don’t know, what is the worst thing among
human beings.

00:46:36.264 --> 00:46:46.754
According to Krishna it was ‘temper – hot temper’
was the worst thing. But according to Me it

00:46:46.754 --> 00:46:50.954
is ‘jealousy.’

00:46:50.954 --> 00:46:57.644
Jealousy of any kind is absolutely, I should
say, like a scum.

00:46:57.644 --> 00:47:05.974
In Sahaja Yoga also people feel jealous, and
they may not say so, because I don’t like

00:47:05.974 --> 00:47:13.814
it, but they may create a problem.
They may try to create problem among each other.

00:47:13.814 --> 00:47:20.164
So one thing you should have a watch on your
mind if there is any kind of jealousy.

00:47:20.164 --> 00:47:27.694
I’m rather worried sometimes. Supposing
I want to give some present to some people,

00:47:27.694 --> 00:47:34.744
then I’m worried that I shouldn’t do something
that will create jealousy.

00:47:34.744 --> 00:47:38.744
We should not.

00:47:38.744 --> 00:47:45.724
Mother might have forgotten or, it’s alright,
She is running short of it, it’s alright.

00:47:45.724 --> 00:47:53.404
But people have that kind of a very sharp
sense of jealousy even in Sahaja Yoga.

00:47:53.404 --> 00:47:59.174
Now supposing I meet somebody and I don’t
meet somebody else - finished!

00:47:59.174 --> 00:48:04.434
That person develops a jealousy for
the person whom I meet.

00:48:04.434 --> 00:48:08.354
Sometimes people pester me too much.
“Mother, I must meet you, I must meet you”.

00:48:08.354 --> 00:48:11.104
I don’t know why. Why do you want to meet
Me?

00:48:11.104 --> 00:48:16.704
I’m all over, everywhere as you say.

00:48:16.704 --> 00:48:22.234
Then what is the need that you should meet
me and talk to Me, what is the need?

00:48:22.234 --> 00:48:29.764
It’s not for you alone, I am, I am for everyone,
but some people think that they have a special

00:48:29.764 --> 00:48:37.134
right on Me and they think that I must meet
them, individually. Otherwise they feel very

00:48:37.134 --> 00:48:38.134
bad.

00:48:38.134 --> 00:48:45.974
All these things have to go away in a big
way when you become, as I said - the ocean.

00:48:45.974 --> 00:48:53.264
Then you are not bothered. What shore you go,
where you travel, you are not bothered. You

00:48:53.264 --> 00:48:57.274
are only with the ocean moving up and down.

00:48:57.274 --> 00:49:05.744
That is how it’s a living ocean of love,
and that’s what we have to develop it. Without

00:49:05.744 --> 00:49:12.264
dominating others, without showing off.

00:49:12.264 --> 00:49:20.274
It should be, the whole thing should be contented
within ourself.

00:49:20.274 --> 00:49:29.394
In Hindi, it is said better: “Apne me samaye hue (अपने में समाए हुए)”

00:49:29.394 --> 00:49:38.344
Should be all within yourself and that’s
the most enjoyable thing!

00:49:38.344 --> 00:49:46.924
Because see, what we want - supposing I want
something for Myself - you see, so I’ll strive

00:49:46.924 --> 00:49:48.404
and get it.

00:49:48.404 --> 00:49:58.274
But this is something, if you have within yourself,
you - fully filled within yourself.

00:49:58.274 --> 00:50:03.314
So what is most important? what is so much
needed?

00:50:03.314 --> 00:50:05.104
Nothing!

00:50:05.104 --> 00:50:18.484
You are completely filled with yourself, contented
with yourself, and then you want to share.

00:50:18.484 --> 00:50:28.124
This is the ideal way of dealing with Sahasrara,
I think, and I am sure a day will come, this

00:50:28.124 --> 00:50:34.704
whole world’s Sahasrara has to be opened
out.

00:50:34.704 --> 00:50:40.994
This is what we have to do it, and we are
not going to disappear into some exclusive

00:50:40.994 --> 00:50:49.384
places that is just for meditation, you can
go there. But not for escaping the world.

00:50:49.384 --> 00:50:50.944
That is not the idea.

00:50:50.944 --> 00:50:58.954
Idea is for meditation, for your growth - it
would be a nice place to go to.

00:50:58.954 --> 00:51:15.654
It is very important to understand how valuable
you are, how remarkably important you are:

00:51:15.654 --> 00:51:24.624
born at this time, got your realisation.
For what?

00:51:24.624 --> 00:51:35.783
To emancipate this world, to transform human
beings, to take whole of this world into the

00:51:35.783 --> 00:51:37.354
realm of God.

00:51:38.094 --> 00:51:40.264
That is what you are here for.

00:51:41.074 --> 00:51:43.164
May God bless you.